      "writtenOn": "2017-09-13T18:54:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "well, that condition isn\u0027t about \"are we still loading\". It\u0027s about \"hasn\u0027t the loading failed yet\"\nI\u0027m not sure if |mAccessWatch| is cleared in thread-safe way, and even if it is, checking if it\u0027s not null could be not thread safe too. iovectors get processed in multiple threads at once, so this check isn\u0027t really correct enough.\n\n+ it should be in the loadRam() function, before doing any calculations.",
      "parentUuid": "c97589bf_5c383057",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 104,
        "startChar": 0,
